{"tid":2051013,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"謝展寰：喉管可能是傳播途經　為穩妥決定撤離沙田瀝源邨祿泉樓部分居民","createTime":"2020-06-04T12:53:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T13:04:08.000Z","uid":64694,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b2583b5b1d3a24be7722ae91af4ba8b816dd081b","tid":2051013,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:53:32.000Z","msg":"沙田瀝源邨祿泉樓再多一名72歲男子初步確診新型肺炎，當局決定疏散祿泉樓2至15樓的「10」及「12」單位住戶，涉及約1百人，需入住檢疫中心。<br />\n<br />\n環境局副局長謝展寰表示，懷疑祿泉樓5宗個案的感染源頭，是來自「12」單位，發現其他感染單位都是與源頭個案同層或樓上樓下單位。雖然到現場視察後，未有發現涉事個案單位的氣喉氣窗有明顯問題，在渠口取走的樣辦亦無病毒，房署檢查其他涉事單位亦未見有問題，但他表示，再多一個初步確診個案來自「12」單位，認為喉管亦可能是一個傳播途經，決定安排居民撤離。<br />\n<br />\n謝展寰表示，「10」及「12」單位中間的馬桶位置氣喉有連接，雖然經此方法傳染的機會不大，但不排除病毒有機會由「12」單位轉移至「10」單位，認為穩妥起見，安排有關單位的住戶撤離，可讓房署檢查和消毒。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示，同層確診個案的單位，在源頭個案的對面，兩個單位的喉管分離，預計最有可能經環境因素傳染，包括大廈出入口的推門及幾個單位的信箱在附近位置，可能經不同途徑傳播。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530174-20200604.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530174-20200604.htm&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5EtVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=1b94e285\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530174-20200604.htm&h=ab43f71c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530174-20200604.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9b5e003529673de68eee8949ea9f246832f7be22","tid":2051013,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:53:58.000Z","msg":"沙士淘大重現？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c6df43628fec14d5b03123d59be17eaa2a42c0b","tid":2051013,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:54:28.000Z","msg":"哇，連登更新咗之後出埋條link嘅縮圖，正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31fa7ccfdaa4167d949292237db6ecbae2e8a533","tid":2051013,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:55:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e52e019b1a0ae76f60ec810ef4891eae712fe552","tid":2051013,"uid":7043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:59:28.000Z","msg":"呢d真係防不勝防<br />\n邊諗到出街戴晒口罩消晒毒<br />\n然後俾屋企條喉玩起左<br />\n真係命運黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed54448ef593fbb33b814bfd2a8bda0866dc1ff0","tid":2051013,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T13:04:08.000Z","msg":"起初青衣都係<br />\n<br />\n時間證明左結果係點"}]}